ConstValues.value: "Recite Alif and Hamzah without any elongation. Stretch two-component letters for the length of one Alif. Stretch three-component letters for the length of three Alifs (such as Ayn, Nun, Waw). These letters form the foundation of Qur'an learning, so it is essential to recognize them clearly."
"Sounds like sa. Put the tongue in the middle of your front teeth (upper and lower). The teeth will touch the tongue slightly."
